lead_paragraph: The president of the Spanish Olympic committee (COE), Alejandro Blanco, has reassured the country's athletes and fans traveling to Rio de Janeiro that the Zika virus "is under control".

headline.print_headline: Spain's Olympic President Blanco Calms Fears Over Zika
